trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <xref uid="langword_csharp_Command" name="Command" href=""></xref> event.
trans-unit.target: Tillhandahåller data för den <xref uid="langword_csharp_Command" name="Command" href=""> </xref> händelse.

trans-unit.source: The `Command` event is raised when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton>, or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> control button in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField> object is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Den `Command` händelsen inträffar när en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton>, eller <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton>kontrollknapp i en <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField>objektet klickas.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPagerField> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LinkButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.ImageButton> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Button>

trans-unit.source: The DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs class is used internally by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.OnBubbleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField.HandleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> methods to access information about the event that was raised.
trans-unit.target: Klassen DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs används internt av den <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.OnBubbleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>och <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField.HandleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoder för att komma åt information om händelsen skapades.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.TemplatePagerField.HandleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.DataPager.OnBubbleEvent%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.target: En lista över inledande egenskapsvärden för en instans av klassen DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs, finns i konstruktorn DataPagerFieldCommandEventArgs.
